OL,3,CSchool leaders say Stormont's three-
OL,4,Cyear budget is 'completely unrealistic'
OL,6,FSchool leaders from across the
OL,7,Feducation sector have described
OL,8,FStormont's draft Three-Year Budget as
OL,9,F"completely unrealistic".
OL,11,FFor those leading the teaching
OL,12,Fprofession, the job is getting harder
OL,13,Fwith financial pressures growing. Now
OL,14,Fspeaking with one voice, several
OL,15,Fassociations representing heads and
OL,16,Fgovernors say Stormont's proposed
OL,17,Fbudget will only make things worse.
