OL,3,CSchool leaders say Stormont's three-
OL,4,Cyear budget is 'completely unrealistic'
OL,6,FFiona Kane, St. Ronan's College
OL,7,FPrinciple said: "We'll always look for
OL,8,Fcost savings in our work and in areas
OL,9,Fthat we could trim back if there's
OL,10,Fsurplus.
OL,12,F"However, we're talking about core
OL,13,Fprovision right now, and we're just
OL,14,Fvery concerned that we're not even
OL,15,Fgoing to be able to meet our core
OL,16,Fprovision based on the three-year
OL,17,Fplan."
