OL,3,CSchool leaders say Stormont's three-
OL,4,Cyear budget is 'completely unrealistic'
OL,6,FOver 70% of schools are already
OL,7,Frunning at a deficit, not to mention
OL,8,Fthe projected departmental overspend
OL,9,Fof #250 million.
OL,11,FThe Education Minister has previously
OL,12,Fwarned the draft budget will see
OL,13,Fdevastating cuts.
OL,15,FThere's no executive agreement on
OL,16,Fthose proposals, and Paul Givan says
OL,17,Fhe plans to meet the Finance Minister
OL,18,Fthis week.
