OL,3,CSchool leaders say Stormont's three-
OL,4,Cyear budget is 'completely unrealistic'
OL,6,FPaul Givan MLA, Education Minister
OL,7,Fsaid: "He decided to put that out to
OL,8,Fpublic consultation, and I think he's
OL,9,Fgetting the reaction which I
OL,10,Fanticipated, particularly from our
OL,11,Fschool leaders, as they realize the
OL,12,Fdevastating consequences that it would
OL,13,Fhave for our school system."
OL,15,FStaffing is the biggest expenditure
OL,16,Ffor schools. While no one wants to see
OL,17,Fredundancies, headteachers have
OL,18,Fsuggested further cuts could see
OL,19,Flarger class sizes, shorter days, and
OL,20,Freduced subject choices.
