OL,6,FFiona Kane continued: "I don't want to
OL,7,Fbe a school that is suggesting that we
OL,8,Fsend young people home because it
OL,9,Fsaves us money.
OL,11,F"I want to maintain what we're doing.
OL,12,FI think we do a good job.
OL,14,F"I think our parents are happy; our
OL,15,Fyoung people are thriving and they're
OL,16,Fsuccessful.
