OL,3,CSchool leaders say Stormont's three-
OL,4,Cyear budget is 'completely unrealistic'
OL,6,FSchool leaders are now calling on the
OL,7,Fpublic to make their views known on
OL,8,Fthe draft budget through the
OL,9,Fconsultation process.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,12,FFinance said: "The Draft Budget
OL,13,Fproposals brought forward have been
OL,14,Fdeveloped against the backdrop of an
OL,15,Fexceptionally constrained financial
OL,16,Fposition and therefore do not provide
OL,17,Fthe level of funding the Finance
OL,18,FMinister would wish to see directed at
OL,19,Four public services; instead, they
OL,20,Freflect what is possible within the
OL,21,Ffunding available.
