OL,6,F"In this context it is simply not
OL,7,Fpossible to provide any department
OL,8,Fwith the funding it has requested.
OL,9,FMinister O'Dowd has been clear that
OL,10,Fadequate funding is required from
OL,11,FWestminster for investment in public
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,F"The Finance Minister is committed to
OL,15,Fworking constructively with his
OL,16,FMinisterial colleagues and will be
OL,17,Fundertaking a series of Budget
OL,18,Fbilateral meetings to continue
OL,19,Fdiscussions in relation to the Draft
OL,20,FBudget to find a way forward."
